Studio apartment in the best Location in Tel Aviv, Hamelech Koresh St., a street parallel to Rothschild, close to Shnkin, close to the TLV mall, a quiet and central area in the apartment, equipment with refrigerator, stove, air conditioner, TV, bed, and more Rent 3,200 NIS, property tax about 180 for two months, electricity and water according to consumption.
